"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Eigenspace/Basic.html#Module.End.genEigenspace\"><span class=\"name\">Module</span>.<span class=\"name\">End</span>.<span class=\"name\">genEigenspace</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">R</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> v}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">M</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> w}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Ring/Defs.html#CommRing\">CommRing</a> <span class=\"fn\">R</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.html#AddCommGroup\">AddCommGroup</a> <span class=\"fn\">M</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Module/Defs.html#Module\">Module</a> <span class=\"fn\">R</span> <span class=\"fn\">M</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Module/LinearMap/End.html#Module.End\">End</a> <span class=\"fn\">R</span> <span class=\"fn\">M</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">μ</span> : <span class=\"fn\">R</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/ENat/Defs.html#ENat\">ℕ∞</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Hom/Basic.html#OrderHom\">→o</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Module/Submodule/Defs.html#Submodule\">Submodule</a> <span class=\"fn\">R</span> <span class=\"fn\">M</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The submodule `genEigenspace f μ k` for a linear map `f`, a scalar `μ`,\nand a number `k : ℕ∞` is the kernel of `(f - μ • id) ^ k` if `k` is a natural number,\nor the union of all these kernels if `k = ∞`. (`k = ∞` corresponds to Def 8.19 of [axler2024].)\nA generalized eigenspace for some exponent `k` is contained in\nthe generalized eigenspace for exponents larger than `k`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Eigenspace/Basic.html#Module.End.genEigenspace","kind":"def","line":68,"name":"Module.End.genEigenspace","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Eigenspace/Basic.lean#L68-L75"}}],"imports":["Init","Mathlib.Algebra.Algebra.Spectrum.Basic","Mathlib.Algebra.Module.LinearMap.Basic","Mathlib.LinearAlgebra.FiniteDimensional.Lemmas","Mathlib.LinearAlgebra.GeneralLinearGroup.Basic","Mathlib.RingTheory.Nilpotent.Basic","Mathlib.RingTheory.Nilpotent.Defs","Mathlib.RingTheory.Nilpotent.Lemmas","Mathlib.Tactic.Peel"],"instances":[{"className":"CoeOut","name":"Module.End.UnifEigenvalues.instCoeOut","typeNames":["Module.End.UnifEigenvalues"]},{"className":"Decidable","name":"Module.End.UnivEigenvalues.instDecidableEq","typeNames":["Eq"]}],"name":"Mathlib.LinearAlgebra.Eigenspace.Basic"}